Class Stock

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mycompany.stockswag.StockManager.Stock
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Index

    public class Stock
extends Object
    Represents individual Stocks in StockSwag. historicalData contains date & price pairs starting from newest to oldest in list format. dailyReturns contains %growths starting from oldest. Values in %!
    Author:
    EliAir
